<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Document</title>
  <style>
    .breakPage {
      page-break-after: always;
    }

    .bold {
      color: #1f497d;
      font-size: 12pt;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-family: "Calibri";
      padding: 0 10px;
    }

    .regular {
      color: #1f497d;
      font-size: 12pt;
      font-weight: normal;
      font-family: "Calibri";
      padding: 0 10px;
    }

    .no-margin {
      margin: 0;
    }

    .no-padding {
      padding: 0;
    }

    .regular__min {
      color: #1f497d;
      font-size: 10pt;
      font-weight: normal;
      font-family: "Calibri";
      padding: 0 10px;
    }

    .container {
      page-break-inside: avoid;
    }

    .containerPadding {
      padding: 0px;
    }

    .container__title {
      text-align: end;
      width: 100%;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #6e6e6e;
    }

    .container__title__title {
      color: #023671;
      font-size: 24pt !important;
      font-family: "Calibri";
      font-weight: normal;
    }

    h1.container__title__title {
      margin-bottom: 4px !important;
    }

    h3.container__title__subtitle {
      margin-top: 4px !important;
    }

    .container__title__subtitle {
      color: #023671;
      font-size: 16pt !important;
      font-family: "Calibri";
      font-weight: normal;
    }

    .cellSx {
      text-align: center;
      background-color: #eeeeee !important;
      width: 50%;
    }

    .cellDx {
      text-align: center;
      width: 50%;
    }

    table {
      border: 1px solid #333;
      border-spacing: 0;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }

    td,
    th {
      border: 1px solid #333;
    }

    /* NB */

    .container__nb {
      margin-top: 5px;
      width: 100%;
    }

    /* INDICE */

    .container__contenuti {
      padding-top: 0pt;
      padding-bottom: 0;
    }

    .container__inner_contenuti {
      padding: 1rem;
    }

    .contentuti__row {
      display: flex;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .contenuti__row__sx {
      width: 90%;
      border-bottom: 1px dotted #ccc;
    }

    .contenuti__row__dx {
      width: 10%;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
    }

    /* get by script */
    .table3 {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      table-layout: fixed;
      /*  border: 1px solid white; */
    }

    .table3 th {
      color: black;
    }

    .table3 td {
      color: rgb(0, 0, 0);
    }

    .table3 th,
    .table3 td {
      /* border: none;*/
      /*  border: 1px solid rgb(255, 255, 255); */
      /* Aggiunge un bordo alle celle */
      font-size: 9px;
      /* white-space: nowrap;
      overflow: hidden;
      text-overflow: ellipsis; */
      color: #023671;
    }

    .bkT2 {
      border: none;
      background-color: white;
      color: #023671;
    }

    .bkT1 {
      border: none;
      background-color: #023671;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.932);
    }

    .regular__min {
      text-align: justify;
    }

    .tableBuilding {
      width: 100%;
      border: 0.5px solid black !important;
    }

    .thBuilding {
      text-align: center;
      border: 0.5px solid black !important;
    }

    .pBuilding {
      color: #1f497d !important;
      font-size: x-small;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="container__title">
        <h1 class="container__title__title">Rintraccio Anagrafico</h1>
        <h3 class="container__title__subtitle">Persona fisica</h3>
      </div>
      <!-- TABELLA -->
      <table style="width: 100%; margin-top: 50px">
        {{#if registry.surname}}
        <thead>
          <th colspan="2">
            <p class="bold no-margin" style="text-align: center">
              {{registry.name}} {{registry.surname}}
            </p>
          </th>
        </thead>
        {{/if}}
        <tbody>
          <tr style="border: none">
            <td style="width: 50%; background: #eeeeee">
              <p class="bold no-margin" style="text-align: center">
                INFORMAZIONE N°
              </p>
            </td>
            <td style="width: 50%">
              <p class="regular no-margin" style="text-align: center">
                {{informazioneN}}
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="width: 50%; background: #eeeeee">
              <p class="bold no-margin" style="text-align: center">
                RIF. CLIENTE
              </p>
            </td>
            <td style="width: 50%">
              <p class="regular no-margin" style="text-align: center">
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="width: 50%; background: #eeeeee">
              <p class="bold no-margin" style="text-align: center">
                DATA RICHIESTA
              </p>
            </td>
            <td style="width: 50%">
              <p class="regular no-margin" style="text-align: center">
                {{inputData.dateRequested}}
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="width: 50%; background: #eeeeee">
              <p class="bold no-margin" style="text-align: center">
                DATA EVASIONE
              </p>
            </td>
            <td style="width: 50%">
              <p class="regular no-margin" style="text-align: center">
                {{inputData.dateFulfillment}}
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
      <!-- DATI INPUT -->
      <table style="width: 100%; margin-top: 50px">
        <thead>
          <th colspan="2">
            <p class="bold no-margin" style="text-align: center">
              DATI INPUT
            </p>
          </th>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr style="border: none">
            <td style="width: 50%; background: #eeeeee">
              <p class="bold no-margin" style="text-align: center">COGNOME</p>
            </td>
            <td style="width: 50%">
              <p class="regular no-margin" style="text-align: center">
                {{registry.surname}}
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="width: 50%; background: #eeeeee">
              <p class="bold no-margin" style="text-align: center">NOME</p>
            </td>
            <td style="width: 50%">
              <p class="regular no-margin" style="text-align: center">
                {{registry.name}}
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="width: 50%; background: #eeeeee">
              <p class="bold no-margin" style="text-align: center">
                CODICE FISCALE
              </p>
            </td>
            <td style="width: 50%">
              <p class="regular no-margin" style="text-align: center">
                {{registry.cf}}
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td style="width: 50%; background: #eeeeee">
              <p class="bold no-margin" style="text-align: center">
                COMUNE DI RESIDENZA
              </p>
            </td>
            <td style="width: 50%">
              <p class="regular no-margin" style="text-align: center">
                {{registry.municipality}}
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="width: 50%; background: #eeeeee">
              <p class="bold no-margin" style="text-align: center">
                INDIRIZZO
              </p>
            </td>
            <td style="width: 50%">
              <p class="regular no-margin" style="text-align: center">
                {{registry.address}}
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td style="width: 50%; background: #eeeeee">
              <p class="bold no-margin" style="text-align: center">
                NOME PRODOTTO
              </p>
            </td>
            <td style="width: 50%">
              <p class="regular no-margin" style="text-align: center">
                Rintraccio ANAGRAFICO
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
      <!-- N.B. -->
      <div class="container__nb breakPage">
        <span class="bold">N.B.</span>
        <p class="regular__min">
          Le informazioni ed i dati forniti dalla nostra azienda alla propria
          clientela, sono raccolti e trattati secondo quanto disposto dal D.
          Lgs. 196 del 2003 e dal nuovo RE 679/2016. I clienti possono quindi
          utilizzare i dati e le informazioni fornite secondo le modalità
          previste dalla legge per la tutela dei propri diritti.
          L’informazione ha natura strettamente riservata, personale e
          confidenziale, pertanto non può essere divulgata a terzi e tantomeno
          in sede giudiziaria in quanto le informazioni presenti non sono
          supportate da prove documentali. Ci esimiamo da qualsiasi
          responsabilità consequenziale, di natura civile, penale derivanti da
          dette violazioni. E’ sin da ora escluso qualunque titolo e motivo di
          azione di rivalsa per le notizie fornite.
        </p>
      </div>
      <!-- INDICE -->
      <div class="container__contenuti breakPage">
        <p class="bold">Contenuti</p>
        <div class="container__inner_contenuti">
          <a href="#RIEPILOGO_INDAGINE" style="text-decoration: none">
            <div class="contentuti__row">
              <div class="contenuti__row__sx">
                <p class="regular">RIEPILOGO INDAGINE</p>
              </div>
              <div class="contenuti__row__dx">
                <span class="regular" id="indice_riepilogo_indagine"style="display:none">::RIEPILOGO_INDAGINE</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </a>
          <a href="#ANAGRAFICA" style="text-decoration: none">
            <div class="contentuti__row">
              <div class="contenuti__row__sx">
                <p class="regular">ANAGRAFICA</p>
              </div>
              <div class="contenuti__row__dx">
                <span class="regular"style="display:none">::ANAGRAFICA</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </a>
          <a href="#REPERIBILITÀ" style="text-decoration: none">
            <div class="contentuti__row">
              <div class="contenuti__row__sx">
                <p class="regular">REPERIBILITÀ</p>
              </div>
              <div class="contenuti__row__dx">
                <span class="regular"style="display:none">::REPERIBILITÀ</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </a>
          <a href="#RECAPITI_TELEFONICI" style="text-decoration: none">
            <div class="contentuti__row">
              <div class="contenuti__row__sx">
                <p class="regular">RECAPITI TELEFONICI</p>
              </div>
              <div class="contenuti__row__dx">
                <span class="regular"style="display:none">::RECAPITI_TELEFONICI</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- RIEPILOGO INDAGINE -->
      <div class="container_riepilogo_indagine breakPage" id="RIEPILOGO_INDAGINE">
        <p class="bold" style="border-bottom: 2px solid #6e6e6e">
          :RIEPILOGO INDAGINE
        </p>
        <!-- TABELLA -->
        <table style="width: 100%; margin-top: 25px">
          {{#if registry.surname}}
          <thead>
            <th colspan="2">
              <p class="bold no-margin" style="text-align: center">
                {{registry.name}} {{registry.surname}}
              </p>
            </th>
          </thead>
          {{/if}}
          <tbody>
            <tr style="border: none">
              <td style="width: 50%; background: #eeeeee">
                <a href="#ANAGRAFICA" style="text-decoration: none">
                  <p class="bold no-margin" style="text-align: center">
                    ANAGRAFICA
                  </p>
                </a>
              </td>
              {{#if registry}}
              <td style="width: 50%">
                <p class="regular no-margin" style="text-align: center; color: #008000">
                  PRESENTE
                </p>
              </td>
              {{else}}
              <td style="width: 50%">
                <p class="regular no-margin" style="text-align: center; color: #ff0000">
                  NON PRESENTE
                </p>
              </td>
              {{/if}}
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="width: 50%; background: #eeeeee">
                <a href="#REPERIBILITÀ" style="text-decoration: none">
                  <p class="bold no-margin" style="text-align: center">
                    REPERIBILITÀ
                  </p>
                </a>
              </td>
              {{#if isReperibilita}}
              <td style="width: 50%">
                <p class="regular no-margin" style="text-align: center; color: #008000">
                  CONFERMATA
                </p>
              </td>
              {{else}}
              <td style="width: 50%">
                <p class="regular no-margin" style="text-align: center; color: #ff0000">
                  NON CONFERMATA
                </p>
              </td>
              {{/if}}
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="width: 50%; background: #eeeeee">
                <a href="#RECAPITI_TELEFONICI" style="text-decoration: none">
                  <p class="bold no-margin" style="text-align: center">
                    RECAPITI TELEFONICI
                  </p>
                </a>
              </td>
              {{#if contactPhoneNumber.length}}
              <td style="width: 50%">
                <p class="regular no-margin" style="text-align: center; color: #008000">
                  PRESENTI
                </p>
              </td>
              {{else}}
              <td style="width: 50%">
                <p class="regular no-margin" style="text-align: center; color: #ff0000">
                  NON PRESENTI
                </p>
              </td>
              {{/if}}
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <!-- ANAGRAFICA -->
      <div class="container" id="ANAGRAFICA">
        <p class="bold" style="border-bottom: 2px solid #6e6e6e">
          :ANAGRAFICA
        </p>
        <!-- TABELLA -->
        <table style="width: 100%">
          <tbody>
            <tr style="border: none">
              <td style="width: 50%; background: #eeeeee">
                <p class="bold no-margin" style="text-align: left">
                  COGNOME
                </p>
              </td>
              <td style="width: 50%">
                <p class="regular no-margin" style="text-align: left">
                  {{registry.surname}}
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="width: 50%; background: #eeeeee">
                <p class="bold no-margin" style="text-align: left">NOME</p>
              </td>
              <td style="width: 50%">
                <p class="regular no-margin" style="text-align: left">
                  {{registry.name}}
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="width: 50%; background: #eeeeee">
                <p class="bold no-margin" style="text-align: left">
                  CODICE FISCALE
                </p>
              </td>
              <td style="width: 50%">
                <p class="regular no-margin" style="text-align: left">
                  {{registry.cf}}
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="width: 50%; background: #eeeeee">
                <p class="bold no-margin" style="text-align: left">
                  DATA DI NASCITA
                </p>
              </td>
              <td style="width: 50%">
                <p class="regular no-margin" style="text-align: left">
                  {{registry.dateOfBirth}}
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="width: 50%; background: #eeeeee">
                <p class="bold no-margin" style="text-align: left">
                  LUOGO DI NASCITA
                </p>
              </td>
              <td style="width: 50%">
                <p class="regular no-margin" style="text-align: left">
                  {{registry.placeOfBirth}}
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="width: 50%; background: #eeeeee">
                <p class="bold no-margin" style="text-align: left">
                  PROVINCIA DI NASCITA
                </p>
              </td>
              <td style="width: 50%">
                <p class="regular no-margin" style="text-align: left">{{registry.provinceOfBirth}}</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="width: 50%; background: #eeeeee">
                <p class="bold no-margin" style="text-align: left">
                  INDIRIZZO
                </p>
              </td>
              <td style="width: 50%">
                <p class="regular no-margin" style="text-align: left">
                  {{registry.address}}
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="width: 50%; background: #eeeeee">
                <p class="bold no-margin" style="text-align: left">CAP</p>
              </td>
              <td style="width: 50%">
                <p class="regular no-margin" style="text-align: left">
                  {{registry.cap}}
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="width: 50%; background: #eeeeee">
                <p class="bold no-margin" style="text-align: left">
                  COMUNE
                </p>
              </td>
              <td style="width: 50%">
                <p class="regular no-margin" style="text-align: left">
                  {{registry.municipality}}
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="width: 50%; background: #eeeeee">
                <p class="bold no-margin" style="text-align: left">
                  PROVINCIA
                </p>
              </td>
              <td style="width: 50%">
                <p class="regular no-margin" style="text-align: left">{{registry.province}}</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
             {{#each domicile as |dom|}}
            <tr>
              <td style="width: 50%; background: #eeeeee">
                <p class="bold no-margin" style="text-align: left">
                  INDIRIZZO (DOMICILIO)
                </p>
              </td>
              <td style="width: 50%">
                <p class="regular no-margin" style="text-align: left">{{dom.address}}</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="width: 50%; background: #eeeeee">
                <p class="bold no-margin" style="text-align: left">
                  CAP (DOMICILIO)
                </p>
              </td>
              <td style="width: 50%">
                <p class="regular no-margin" style="text-align: left">{{dom.postalCode}}</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="width: 50%; background: #eeeeee">
                <p class="bold no-margin" style="text-align: left">
                  COMUNE (DOMICILIO)
                </p>
              </td>
              <td style="width: 50%">
                <p class="regular no-margin" style="text-align: left">{{dom.common}}</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="width: 50%; background: #eeeeee">
                <p class="bold no-margin" style="text-align: left">
                  PROVINCIA (DOMICILIO)
                </p>
              </td>
              <td style="width: 50%">
                <p class="regular no-margin" style="text-align: left">{{dom.province}}</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            {{/each}}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <!-- REPERIBILITA -->
      <div class="container" id="REPERIBILITÀ">
        <p class="bold" style="border-bottom: 2px solid #6e6e6e">
          :REPERIBILITÀ
        </p>
        {{#if availability.length}}
          {{#each availability as |ava|}}
          {{#if (isReperibilita)}}
          <p class="regular">
            A seguito
            delle indagini effettuate abbiamo constatato che il richiesto domicilia di fatto al seguente indirizzo:
          </p>
          <table style="width: 100%; border: none !important">
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td style="border: none !important">
                  <p class="regular no-margin">{{ava}}</p>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
            {{else}}
            <p class="regular">
              {{ava}}
            </p>
          {{/if}}
          {{/each}}
          {{else}}
          <p class="regular">
            A seguito
            delle indagini effettuate abbiamo constatato che il richiesto non domicilia presso l'indirizzo di residenza.
            Allo
            stato attuale, nonostante le ricerche effettuate ad ampissimo raggio, non è stato possibile rintracciare il
            luogo
            dove sia reperibile.
          </p>
          {{/if}}
      </div>
      <!-- RECAPITI TELEFONICI -->
      <div class="container" id="RECAPITI_TELEFONICI" class="breakPage">
        <p class="bold" style="border-bottom: 2px solid #6e6e6e">
          :RECAPITI TELEFONICI
        </p>
        {{#if contactPhoneNumber.length}}
        <p class="regular">
          A seguito delle indagini effettuate, abbiamo constatato che il richiesto è
          reperibile alle seguenti utenze telefoniche:
        </p>
        {{else}}
        <p class="regular">
          A seguito delle indagini effettuate, abbiamo constatato che il richiesto non è
          reperibile ad alcuna utenza telefonica attiva a lui collegata
        </p>
        <table style="width: 100%; border: none !important">
          <tbody>
            {{#each contactPhoneNumber as |num|}}
            <tr>
              {{#if num.fixed}}
              <td style="border: none !important">
                <p class="regular no-margin">Telefono fisso: {{num.contact}}</p>
                <p class="regular no-margin">{{num.note}}</p>
              </td>
              {{else}}
              <td style="border: none !important">
                <p class="regular no-margin">Telefono mobile: {{num.contact}}</p>
                <p class="regular no-margin">{{num.note}}</p>
              </td>
              {{/if}}
            </tr>
            {{/each}}
          </tbody>
        </table>        
        {{/if}}
        <table style="width: 100%; border: none !important">
          <tbody>
            {{#each notePhoneNumber as |ntel|}}
            <tr>
              <td style="border: none !important">
                <p class="regular no-margin">{{ntel.note}}</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            {{/each}}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>